<p style="font-family: 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Um bom 2014 pra tod@s!</span><img src="/articles/0132/1236/brasil.png" alt="" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p>
